Yahoo Japan Rises Most in Four Months on Yahoo Inc. Sale Report

-- B y   G e a r o i d   R e i d y
-- 
2011-03-02T00:34:56Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-02/yahoo-japan-rises-most-in-four-months-on-yahoo-inc-sale-report.html
  Yahoo Japan Corp . rose the most in
almost four months in Tokyo trading after Reuters reported that
Yahoo Inc. is in talks to sell its 35 percent stake in the
Japanese company.  Yahoo Japan gained 6.1 percent to 33,050 yen as of 9:31
a.m. on the Tokyo Stock Exchange, headed for the biggest climb
since Oct. 14. The benchmark Nikkei 225 Stock Average fell 1.7
percent.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Gearoid Reidy at 
 greidy1@bloomberg.net  